* Policy Inheritance\n& Scope
** Inheritance model
***_ Catalog → Schemas → Tables
***_ Schema → Tables
***_ Tag new table = auto-protected
** Policy quotas
***_ 10 policies per catalog
***_ 10 policies per schema
***_ 5 policies per table
** Conflict rules
***_ Only 1 row filter per table
***_ Only 1 column mask per column
***_ Conflict → access blocked + error
** Runtime requirement
***_ DBR 16.4+ or serverless
***_ Non-policy users: any runtime
@endmindmap
